OnePlus has built a reputation for delivering premium features at competitive prices, and the OnePlus 13 Pro continues this legacy. It combines sleek design with outstanding performance.

**Key Features:**  
- **Display:** 6.7-inch Fluid AMOLED with a vibrant 120Hz refresh rate.  
